{"tid":958501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新年加人工】紐約州大除夕調高最低工資 時薪加至15元","createTime":"2018-12-28T00:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T02:58:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba09a5e1935ddbd90988a3cbe02c842a626a6cce","tid":958501,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T00:49:31.000Z","msg":"【新年加人工】紐約州大除夕調高最低工資 時薪加至15元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181227/59074185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59074185&d=71pwVW65x16IUdXCvZTcCARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=24b580f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59074185&h=43f3a780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181227/59074185</a><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）紐約州州長科莫（Andrew Cuomo）宣佈，全州僱員的最低時薪，將於12月31日大除夕上調。其中，紐約市大企業僱員的最低工資，將上調至每小時15元（美元，下同；約117.5港元）。州政府設「薪金小偷熱線」，供僱員舉報未有按規定加薪的僱主。<br />\n<br />\n紐約州於2016年至2017年度的州財政預算案中，通過將州內各地區最低時薪，分階段上調至15元，其中在紐約市，僱用11人或以上的企業，被歸類為大企業，最低時薪在2016年大除夕為11元，去年上調至13元，本月31日將率先調高至「達標」的15元。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市10人或以下機構的最低時薪，將上調至13.5元，明年大除夕上調至15元；長島與威斯特徹斯特縣（Westchester）將上調至12元，未來三年每年上調1元，至2021年達標；紐約州其餘地區的最低時薪，則將上調至11.1元，至2020年大除夕上調至12.5元，最終上調至15元的時間表未定。<br />\n<br />\n州政府將透過電視、數碼平台、電台和地鐵廣告，宣傳有關措施。州勞工局設立熱線1-888-NYSDOL，供領取最低工資的僱員，舉報未有按照時間表加薪的僱主。查詢詳情，<a href=\"http://可瀏覽官方網頁www.ny.gov/minimumwage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AF%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81www.ny.gov%2Fminimumwage&d=71pwVW65x16IUdXCvZTcCARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ccd854e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">可瀏覽官方網頁www.ny.gov/minimumwage</a>"},{"pid":"c98c2446d59797395b851c6ea3c03cdd89450fdf","tid":958501,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T00:51:25.000Z","msg":"咁好揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225bc6b4fc69e29cfaeb3fca894d373c6a1292cd","tid":958501,"uid":82851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我拎萬二 未扣mpf已經滿足"},{"pid":"ea199f356ac5fd588037d8aedc85bd45e8cd3883","tid":958501,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"香港跟隨 調整至時薪十五<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">港</span></span>元"},{"pid":"c5b4d2360fbb202163ab664bbe4af6c56f406c8e","tid":958501,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"大公司又有機會加價，仲會加突，物價又反而變貴咗<br />\n因為額外調整產品費用同人工，全部都係成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有加人工 = 冇加"},{"pid":"1f2cbc52733723ec2a1a9a6c47db17257f4d1c6c","tid":958501,"uid":51200,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c5b4d2360fbb202163ab664bbe4af6c56f406c8e","tid":958501,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"大公司又有機會加價，仲會加突，物價又反而變貴咗<br />\n因為額外調整產品費用同人工，全部都係成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有加人工 = 冇加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"On 9<br />\n去外國/其他州咪多撚左錢洗囉"},{"pid":"c9be589ea2a815439eba627d969e739e29f1a6da","tid":958501,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"香港：調整每日最低工作時數至15個鐘"},{"pid":"1042134d7a3839b4754f51de5b832a49aba5854c","tid":958501,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"咁高 minimum wage, 點解前線人員仲要靠 tips 維生?"},{"pid":"21d107c4916710ca2426a9740b1d79058385de9d","tid":958501,"uid":226126,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a05cfa88c87b54399075992a3495974d851adf8a","tid":958501,"uid